O-lang / ^Olang_: the Ouroboros Language
Copyright 2026 Lee Daghlar Ostadi

Original public implementation:
https://github.com/lostadi/Olang

Core contribution:
Typed expression boundaries, where the evaluator of an expression is part of
the expression syntax:

    LANG^( body )_LANG

Associated project terms:
O-lang, ^Olang_, Ouroboros Language, OValue, OIR, O-core, typed parentheses,
evaluator-as-syntax, language-boundary calculus, "the nesting is the interface."

This project and its documentation originate with Lee Daghlar Ostadi.
